This is the second version of Sukma, now using the Breton Race rather than Breton Child Race from RS Children, more cute and mature!
[/size][size=5](〃‿〃✿)[/size][/center]

[center][img]https://image.ibb.co/exbJGy/Capturese.jpg[/img]﻿[/center][size=4]But first I want to clarify something, I do not steal from another mod, I've made Sukma for a long time, I made her based on the face of my junior school friend, version 1.0 using Children Race from RS Children and looks like a doll and childish, so I want to make her more mature up by importing her old preset into the Breton Race with little change. [list=1]
[*]Download this mod manually.
[*]Extract the contents somewhere, like your desktop as an example
[*]Drag and drop the trislot file into Documents/My Games/Skyrim/CME_save
